<h2>Campaign Design API</h2>
<p>The Maxymiser Campaign Design API is a JavaScript API that allows you to design testing campaigns in order to optimise the content on your site pages.</p>
<p>Guide:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="cd-api/overview/">Campaign Design API Overview Video</a></li>
  <li><a href="cd-api/guide/">Campaign Design Javascript API Guide</a></li>
  <li><a href="cd-api/reference/">Campaign Design Javascript API Reference</a></li>
  <li><a href="cd-api/changelog/">Campaign Design API Changelog</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Applications:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="cd-api/visitor-tracking/">How to Properly Track a Visitor's Behavior</a></li>
  <li><a href="cd-api/single-page-routing-module/">Using CD API on Single Page Applications</a></li>
  <li><a href="cd-api/react-module/">Using CD API on React Content</a></li>
  <li><a href="cd-api/cross-domain/">CD API Cross-Domain Visitor ID Transfer</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Cookies:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="cd-api/cookies/">Oracle Maxymiser Cookies Explained</a></li>
  <li><a href="cd-api/cookies-optimization/">Reducing Maxymiser's Cookies Size</a></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<h2>Campaign Design API Integrations</h2>
<p>Sending and receiving data with 3rd party platforms.</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="integrations/overview/">Integrations Overview</a></li>
  <li><a href="integrations/adobe-analytics/">Adobe Analytics Integration</a></li>
  <li><a href="integrations/clicktale/">Clicktale Integration</a></li>
  <li><a href="integrations/demandbase/">Demandbase Integration</a></li>
  <li><a href="integrations/google-analytics/">Google Universal Analytics Integration</a></li>
  <li><a href="integrations/heap-analytics/">Heap Analytics Integration</a></li>
  <li><a href="integrations/ibm-analytics/">IBM Analytics Integration</a></li>
  <li><a href="integrations/sessioncam/">SessionCam Integration</a></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<h2>REST API</h2>
<p>The Oracle Maxymiser REST API makes it possible to access Maxymiser's platform functionality with code. You can use it to manage campaign entities, such as Elements, Variants, Actions and Scripts programmatically.</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://docs.oracle.com/cloud/latest/marketingcs_gs/OMCGF/Overview.html">REST API Overview</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://docs.oracle.com/cloud/latest/marketingcs_gs/OMCGF/rest-endpoints.html">REST API Reference</a></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<h2>Campaign Delivery API</h2>
<p>The Oracle Maxymiser Campaign Delivery API allows you to deliver Maxymiser campaigns and track customer actions programmatically. It can be used to run campaigns server-side, on any networked devices, and on pages which donâ€™t have the Maxymiser tag on them.</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://docs.oracle.com/cloud/latest/marketingcs_gs/OMCGC/Overview.html">Campaign Delivery API Overview</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://docs.oracle.com/cloud/latest/marketingcs_gs/OMCGC/rest-endpoints.html">Campaign Delivery API Reference</a></li>
</ul>
